{"tid":2017524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【澳洲企硬】　堅持推動獨立武漢肺炎病毒源頭調查！","createTime":"2020-05-15T06:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T04:18:27.000Z","uid":124021,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ead8aab8ac837a343c714ee0b1ac7558f13197af","tid":2017524,"uid":124021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:53:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">澳洲總理對北京企硬　堅持推動新冠病毒源頭調查</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳洲因推動對新冠病毒源頭調查而惹怒中國，總理莫理遜（Scott Morrison）<span style=\"color: red;\">今日強調，即使要在貿易關係上付出代價，也會堅持自己的立場。</span><br />\n<br />\n莫理遜(ScoMo)早前推動對新冠病毒源頭的全球獨立調查，被北京批評是美國的爪牙。<br />\n<br />\n自此中國對澳洲動作頻頻，先有駐澳大使成競業稱，中國消費者可能會抵制澳洲的服務和產品；之後中國政府威脅要向澳洲大麥徵收關稅，最近幾日更禁止4間屠場的牛肉進口到中國──雖然中國外交部聲稱此舉與抗疫調查無關。<br />\n<br />\n莫理遜今日（5月15日）在坎培拉向記者表示：「<span style=\"color: orange;\">我們一向都是獨立的。我們一向都追求我們的國家利益，將來都會。」</span><br />\n<br />\n// <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">當談及我們相信和捍衛的價值時，我們會一直堅持自己的立場。</span></strong> //<br />\n<br />\n內政部長達頓（Peter Dutton）也表明，<span style=\"color: red;\">即使與中國的關係緊張，也會繼續推動新冠病毒獨立調查。</span><br />\n<br />\n他多番強調，病毒受害人的家屬有合理的問題需要以透明的方式解答，「澳洲只是堅持自己的立場，我們會一直這樣做。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>工黨亦支持獨立調查</strong><br />\n<br />\n在野工黨亦支持政府推動獨立調查的立場，但批評政府在澳中關係方面發出的訊息。<br />\n<br />\n工黨外交事務發言人黃英賢（Penny Wong）表示，總理應該引領辯論，並且令辯論更清晰和一致。她說：「多遺憾看到這辯論多由保守的後排議員定調和引領，他們爭相向中國發砲。」黃英賢認為，這些言論只是說給本地人聽，「從總理開始，我們要少想本地政治利益。我們要專注在國家利益。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hev1wdU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHev1wdU.jpg&h=1ecd3771&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c4990bc57a9df13c59f29b2cb6b8945db13b5eb","tid":2017524,"uid":124021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:53:50.000Z","msg":"Source : <a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/pm-declared-australia-will-always-stand-its-ground-even-if-it-comes-at-the-cost-of-trade-relations-with-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Fpm-declared-australia-will-always-stand-its-ground-even-if-it-comes-at-the-cost-of-trade-relations-with-china&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=b55bae33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/pm-declared-australia-will-always-stand-its-ground-even-if-it-comes-at-the-cost-of-trade-relations-with-china</a><br />\n<br />\nSBS Cantonese"},{"pid":"c1bff3530ae9210ae9482bfc4d26eb6a8a2db225","tid":2017524,"uid":124021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a6e1b2311ca3869b9e1368ef0ce6e78bee84bf","tid":2017524,"uid":32220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:55:31.000Z","msg":"澳洲一定有美國支持都先會企硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655f093893ee6370a64b5e1beb2c420b97b92929","tid":2017524,"uid":124021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:58:48.000Z","msg":"支持獨立調查！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00aedea458bcaa0c62f15023fbdf805de2636b01","tid":2017524,"uid":124021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:59:31.000Z","msg":"上一篇：調查：近九成澳洲人認為中國隱瞞疫情<br />\n大多數澳洲人認為，中國在處理新冠病毒疫情時有所隱瞞，並且相信中國未來對澳洲國家利益構成風險。<br />\nLink: 調查：近九成澳洲人認為中國隱瞞疫情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2014137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2014137</a>"},{"pid":"1ee65e1a40d83f0be5d03d460064043f66465170","tid":2017524,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep